Overall casualties up to 50,000<sup id="cite_ref-17" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-17">[17]</a></sup><br />
<b>France:</b> 10,000 battle deaths (75% at sea) <b>Spain:</b> 5,000 killed</p>
<b>Netherlands:</b> 500 killed<sup id="cite_ref-18" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-18">[18]</a></sup></td>
