<li><a href="/wiki/Action_of_14_September_1779" title="Action of 14 September 1779">14 September 1779</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Flamborough_Head" title="Battle of Flamborough Head">Flamborough Head</a></li>
