<li id="cite_note-196"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-196">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=zc5ZwyqzpQQC&amp;pg=PA298&amp;dq=parliamentary+register+1780&amp;hl=en&amp;sa=X&amp;ei=M-rPVO-pMrT7sASv6oCgCw&amp;ved=0CCUQ6AEwAQ#v=onepage&amp;q&amp;f=false">Parliamentary Register</a> (1781), pp. 263–65.</span></li>
